Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang di depan layar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memakai media sosial?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, coba bayangkan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana jika kau mati?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan terjadi\Npada akun media sosialmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.06,0:00:25.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kini, jumlah akun orang yang meninggal\Ndi seluruh dunia meningkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.56,0:00:27.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dikenal sebagai "Akun Mati".
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.82,0:00:30.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu takkan diperbarui lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa akan dibiarkan tak tersentuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa tak semudah itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.70,0:00:41.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuatu yang merepotkan\Nmungkin terjadi selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lezat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.70,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ini berlebihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.78,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ini konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.79,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sanggup menontonnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.12,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Itu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.00,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aoringo terlalu buruk.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.25,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pemancing hujatan itu memang berengsek.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menontonnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Video Aoringo tempo hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.05,0:02:57.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melihatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Video saat dia menyergap\Nrumah streamer petarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana bisa dia memukuli orang\Nlalu kabur?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia parah banget. Sampah masyarakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sejujurnya, dia punya banyak penonton.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga salah satunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyebalkan karena aku\Nmeningkatkan jumlah penontonnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku tak tahan untuk mengekliknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Heboh sekali…
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah berlangganan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan hujatannya ramai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.33,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Makin dihujat, makin banyak uangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uang terus masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa berhenti tersenyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yakin sudah boleh bangun?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau tak istirahat…
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji terlalu khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.56,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kondisiku lumayan hari ini. Tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, kau dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak membalas pesanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku ada urusan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, aku beli kue.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang mau kue, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar. Aku juga mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kita sudah sepakat?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya satu pencuci mulut sehari.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berapa banyak yang kau makan hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enam.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau makan dengan benar?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau butuh diet seimbang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bergadang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cucianmu pasti menumpuk lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus jemur futonmu sesekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku mengerti.\N- Bahkan ventilasi lebih penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sulit dipercaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak bisa lakukan apa pun tanpa aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.99,0:04:43.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itulah…
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku menyita kuemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tak adil.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.87,0:04:53.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.96,0:04:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bel perawat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku, Kak Soji.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.05,0:05:10.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kesehatanku seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertahanlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan ke Amerika sebulan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dokter terkenal di sana\Nakan melakukan operasi terbaik untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan segera sembuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yakin soal uangnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis bodoh,\Nkau tak perlu mengkhawatirkan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah sudah kubilang?\NAku temukan pekerjaan bergaji besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan saja pada kakakmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.22,0:05:49.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Jangan jalani hidup\Nyang menyusahkan orang lain."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu yang selalu dikatakan pria tua\Ndari panti asuhan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika bisa menghasilkan banyak uang\Ndengan cara halal, aku pasti mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tak punya bakat atau pengetahuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya kuat dan pandai berkelahi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengganggu? Aku tahu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak peduli jika dibenci\Noleh seluruh umat manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama Akari membaik,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, kumohon…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,biarkan hujatannya ramai!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lama sejak Aoringo\Nmengunggah video baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar dia pensiun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah? Kapan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekitar sebulan lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia dibawa ke Akademi Miden, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.93,0:06:40.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekolah untuk anak bermasalah yang diklaim\Nbisa pulihkan kecanduan ponsel.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya itu sekolah penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah terdaftar, tak ada jalan kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu hanya legenda urban?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Puding ini lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.53,0:06:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pencuci mulut toserba\Nzaman sekarang tak bisa diremehkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lumayan enak untuk masuk peringkat ke-15…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, yang ke-14 di peringkat pudingku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa Akari juga akan menyukai ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.08,0:07:47.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah, sungguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menghindar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar berengsek.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini? Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.73,0:08:09.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sengaja mengumpat\Nseperti "berengsek".
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu intinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini rumahku…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pembunuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan pria itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria itu mengincar ponselku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menelepon polisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, apa maumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kuperjelas, ini pembelaan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuai dugaan, dia incar ponselku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soji Enishiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.64,0:09:27.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,MyuTuber pemancing hujatan, Aoringo, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah melihat videomu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski aku tak pernah mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar merasa jijik.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.53,0:09:38.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan kenangannya memuakkan, Berengsek!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sengaja\Nmenggunakan kata vulgar lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.00,0:09:44.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akulah yang harus minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kerabat orang\Nyang pernah kupukuli, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melakukan itu demi uang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar orang dendam padaku karena itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku siap terima konsekuensinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku belum boleh mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pukul aku sebanyak yang kau mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tolong jangan ambil ponselku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kirim pesan ke adikku\Nyang tak bisa kutemui karena jauh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh kehilangan kontak dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, apa kau dengar?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah sudah kubilang\Njangan sentuh ponselku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berengsek, serahkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.53,0:10:22.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lampiaskan kepadaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak peduli apa yang terjadi kepadamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus hancurkan ponsel itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.04,0:10:30.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku butuh untuk hubungi adikku…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.54,0:10:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu apa yang kau katakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Adikmu…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah dia sudah meninggal sebulan lalu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia belum meninggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, katakan siapa\Nyang mengirimiku pesan sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pasti Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa lagi kalau bukan adikku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Periksa tanda vitalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Stabilkan kakinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.70,0:11:09.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pukul 17.19,\Ndia dinyatakan meninggal dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.05,0:11:21.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa menerimanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bahkan tak menghadiri pemakamannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana mungkin ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana mungkin itu Akari?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan cuma makan manis-manis.\NJangan lupa makan sayur juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.93,0:12:06.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ingat saat kita menjahili\Nmobil Bu Yamada saat SD?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan orang yang menirunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hore!\N- Itu jelas-jelas
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Gaya Akari adalah\N- Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,- tidak mengulang.\N- Dia satu-satunya
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kirimi aku foto kucing.\N- keluargaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suara itu… Akari?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.12,0:12:34.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa… Aku bisa melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga. Dia masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak tahu cara kerjanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Akari masih hidup di dalam ponsel.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus bergegas…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus segera hancurkan ponsel itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak rusak.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah melindungiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa… Aku bisa melihatmu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah membesarkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Akari?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minggir!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.03,0:13:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan adikmu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Akari…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau bertanya\Nsiapa yang kirim pesan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawabannya hantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di toilet.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sumur.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di ruang musik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di pantai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di cermin.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.72,0:14:14.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu selalu muncul di tempat orang mati\Npunya ikatan kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tren era Reiwa adalah "di dalam ponsel".
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu akun media sosial\Norang yang telah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bentuk hantu dari akun mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biasa dikenal sebagai akun gaib.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaib? Kau bercanda!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu mustahil! Itu tak ilmiah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengobrol dengan mendiang adikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong kosong apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.79,0:14:44.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berniat hancurkan ponsel itu\Nsebelum dia jadi akun gaib.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau mengacaukannya, Berengsek!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.89,0:14:50.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu artinya…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari benar-benar…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu dia dalam kondisi itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,serangan fisik begini takkan mempan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saatnya bermain dengan ponsel pintarmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makhluk itu hantu digital.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.08,0:15:17.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tasbih atau salib tradisional\Ntakkan mempan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang mengusir hantu juga harus
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,digitalkan kekuatan spiritual mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia keluarkan palu dari ponselnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otakku tak bisa mengimbangi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.26,0:15:37.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa melihat Banhammer of Civility.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya dia punya bakat cenayang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski kau sampah yang rusak pandangan,\Naku akan perlakukanmu dengan adil.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mengusir adikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia masih punya satu kaki di ponselnya.\NIni waktu tepat untuk bertindak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Civility Brigade!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saatnya akhiri ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang telah mati, kembalilah ke neraka.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.53,0:16:29.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak lihat dia kesakitan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak peduli meski dia hantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya aku bisa bertemu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lakukan ini kepada Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bunuh adikku!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadarlah, Soji Enishiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu mati, kau akan tetap mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak akan pernah bisa hidup kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan hanya kau yang menderita.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sama bagi semua yang ditinggalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,sesulit apa pun,\Nkau harus beradaptasi dan bertahan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, dia kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari, sudah tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisakah kau tenang?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mundur, Berengsek!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, ini gawat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ponselku jatuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa bergerak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku di sini bersamamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begitu, kita bisa bersama selamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.58,0:18:08.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,\NKak Soji tak bisa hidup tanpaku, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.34,0:18:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hantu selalu muncul di tempat orang mati\Npunya ikatan kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.18,0:18:21.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,\NKak Soji tak bisa hidup tanpaku, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.68,0:18:28.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu apa yang kau pegang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau merasa tak bisa meninggalkanku, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau makan puding lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang menahanmu dan membuatmu\Ntak bisa meninggalkan dunia ini
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,ternyata aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aka…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus semangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,ri…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama dengan semua orang yang ditinggalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.51,0:19:02.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesulit apa pun,\Nkau harus beradaptasi dan bertahan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus. Bakar!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakar!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakar…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.83,0:19:30.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Konversi kekuatan spiritual secara digital\Nmelalui ponsel pintar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bangkit di saat genting begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari, kau sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak boleh berada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.14,0:19:48.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi bersama, Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kakak yang tak berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.90,0:19:55.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpamu, aku bahkan\Ntak bisa makan dengan benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan ikuti aturan\Ndan menyantap satu pencuci mulut sehari.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji, ayo…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.66,0:20:08.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan baik-baik saja meski sendirian!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.38,0:20:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Soji.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengandalkanmu, Bu Mina.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kasubata meninggal!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.18,0:21:08.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum mati, Berengsek.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.89,0:21:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Mina membangunkanmu. Bersyukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.69,0:21:19.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah akun gaib yang baru bangkit\Nmudah ditangani Kukuru?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi pria ini\Nmalah mengusir adiknya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyedihkan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku agak terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Kukuru, benarkah katamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia benar-benar bangkit?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia pengusir setan berapi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.75,0:21:38.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, dia tipe penyerang.\NIni yang terburuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan jenis siberkinesis langka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api digitalnya adalah…
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,biru langit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.64,0:21:49.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api Biru Langit? Bukankah itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak, bagaimana dengan pria itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Tentu saja kita bawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa dia kembali ke Akademi Miden.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah itu tempat dia belajar
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau tempat dia mati,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu bergantung padanya.
